definitions.definition: An act of trouncing : a severe beating , a thrashing ; a thorough defeat .

main_definition: An act of trouncing : a severe beating , a thrashing ; a thorough defeat .

definitions.definition: A walk involving some difficulty or effort ; a trek , a tramp , a trudge .
A journey involving quick travel ; also, one that is dangerous or laborious .
